          "reviewBody": "My son is studying in grade -1, I would say the extra care that teachers take here is extremely commendable.. my son didn't know to write in the beginning of the year but now his handwriting has improved a lot.. Class teacher Roopa mam gives individual attention to the kids.\nMy son has developed interest in Hindi Subject because of his Hindi teacher Mili mam..\nThey have just finished their annual day function.. each student was given opportunity to perform on the stage ..\nTheir annual day function was conducted in a well organized manner...",
