          "reviewBody": "Last year my daughter scored 484/500 in class x. The entire coaching was  completely done in school ie. No tuitions or any other additional class. Even though special classes were held regularly no child felt too pressurized. All the teachers were very supportive and friendly. Even though the school timing was long, it felt like a second home to the student. They were given a lot of practice in a calm and relaxed manner.Thanks to the school and the teachers who continuously motivated them throughout the year.",
