          "reviewBody": "Dear , Principal Mam &Teacher,\n\nIt was a great show on Annual function day - 2022, Your management and effort of the students looked amazing. I personally believe that if we want our children physically fit and disciplined then this type of program should be running on regular basis. When I had admitted my Son in this school than I was worried. But now I can say that my Son are in the safe hands. Again congratulations to the Principal ma’am, all organisers and all staff members for organising such a great and memorable program.\n\nRegards\nDiwakar Singh",
